.SH Name
.SP 5 5
is_fighting -  This method determines whether or not the object is fighting another object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int is_fighting(object ob)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - the object being tested
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
1 if it is in combat, 0 if it is not.
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/combat.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method determines whether or not the object is fighting another
object.
